Input & okay from jmc@@
@
text
@.\"	$OpenBSD: tail.1,v 1.22 2015/09/15 19:15:32 schwarze Exp $
.\"	$NetBSD: tail.1,v 1.4 1994/11/23 07:42:13 jtc Exp $
.\"
.\" Copyright (c) 1980, 1990, 1991, 1993
.\"	The Regents of the University of California.  All rights reserved.
